review_blob:
Refreshing and light for an IPA, Great citrus aroma, and a clean finish. Not too hoppy.

Had this at the MN state fair and was completely surprised.

This is the first year I have had a chance to try this beer. I have to say I was completely blown away by the beer I consumed.

I have already purchased 4 more bottles to give to friends to share in the beergasm that this facilitates.
